327
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:13,920
A bit like standing at the board in The Luxury Trap:

328
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:20,280
"I knew I had bad economy but not that it was this bad. "

329
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:22,440
Good summary.

