00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:31,720
Therese clicked on a link, but never entered her details.

332
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:34,920
Kristoffer's computer was infected.

333
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:39,240
The hackers could, after eight hours unlock the computer key chain.

334
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:45,200
